    "## Machine Learning Extensions (`mlxtend`)\n",
    "\n",
    "### Name\n",
    "\n",
    "**Machine Learning Extensions**, commonly shortened to **`mlxtend`**.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Purpose\n",
    "\n",
    "`mlxtend` is a Python library that provides additional machine learning and data science tools beyond those available in `scikit-learn`.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key Features\n",
    "\n",
    "* **Feature Selection**\n",
    "\n",
    "  * Sequential Forward Selection\n",
    "  * Sequential Backward Selection\n",
    "\n",
    "* **Ensemble Learning**\n",
    "\n",
    "  * Stacking Classifiers\n",
    "  * Voting Classifiers\n",
    "\n",
    "* **Data Preprocessing**\n",
    "\n",
    "  * Data scaling\n",
    "  * Data splitting\n",
    "  * Data transformations\n",
    "\n",
    "* **Visualization Utilities**\n",
    "\n",
    "  * Decision region plots\n",
    "  * Learning curves\n",
    "\n",
    "* **Frequent Pattern Mining**\n",
    "\n",
    "  * Association Rules\n",
    "  * Apriori Algorithm\n"
   ]
  },
